      "raw_text": "The S. +. Il N. railroad today lifted\nthe embargo on freight traffic on its\nline, declared on account of the wash\nouts. Everything is now open and\nfreight and passenger traffic will go\nforward as formerly.\n\n\nThe Great Northern reports its line\nopen again clear to st. Paul. Passenger\ntraffic has been interrupted in Dakota\non account of foods. Today all the\ndelayed trains will arrive in Spokane."
